UPDATE 6:00PM 2 JULY 2021 AEST

Congratulations @rosarangel14 and @josephine.barbaro_ You are our lucky CB Lover winners!  Please check your DM! 

🚨🚨 Stay following y'all because I'm going to do another sneaky little story giveaway next week for those still following all our CB Lover sponsors. 👀👀

.
Remember: Winners are chosen randomly by a government audited organisation. They are not chosen based on anyone's financial status, skin colour, location or follower number. We have had winners from USA, Australia, South Africa, Denmark, Puerto Rico, Jamaica, India, New Zealand, Philippines, Germany, Malta, Canada, Bulgaria, Hawaii, Indonesia, Ecuador, Mexico, England, Wales, Ireland, Turkey, Malaysia, Morocco, Venezuela, Peru, Japan, Croatia and now Spain! It could be you next!!

.
We reserve the right to delete and block negative comments. BE NICE!
.

AND several people drawn were ineligible bc you missed or unfollowed some pages or didn’t have your profile set to public !! Remember we now also require your account to be active and in use (so YES you do need to have recent posts to your feed!) This is to crack down on people creating secondary accounts solely to enter our competitions.  We are offering REAL people a chance to win our amazing prizes!
.
Don’t forget : we now also run mini campaigns between our major campaigns to reward those of you who stay following and supporting our amazing sponsors, without them, these campaigns would not be possible!
.

So stay public, stay following or you can't win !!
.

We will see you on 21 JULY 2021 (PST) for another HUGE giveaway with one of our FAVOURITE girls! Stay safe CB lovers!
Permit  TP/00007

🚨🚨Important - We do not follow you or message you from any other account than this one (blue tick verified). Please block, report and ignore any fake accounts pretending to be us. We don't ask for your personal details & we will only contact you on the date of the drawing, if you're a lucky winner! 

Good luck CB Fam! 💁🏼‍♀️🥳
